        public GameProgressObject(int currentLevel,
                          long currentTime,
                          int playerMaxHealth,
                          int playerLifes,
                          int playerMaximumLifes,
                          float playerJumpImpulseVelocity,
                          float playerWalkImpulseVelocity,
                          float playerClimbImpulseVelocity,
                          float playerMaxWalkVelocity,
                          float playerMaxClimbVelocity,
                          int currentlyEquippedWeapon,
                          java.util.ArrayList<WeaponObject> playerWeaponList)
        Parameters:
        currentLevel - the current level which the player is in
        currentTime - the current time in seconds, will remain when the player dies and respawns
        playerMaxHealth - the maximum health that the player can have
        playerLifes - the current amount of player's lifes left
        playerMaximumLifes - the maximum amount of player's lifes
        playerJumpImpulseVelocity - the jumping impulse velocity used in Box2D
        playerWalkImpulseVelocity - the walking impulse velocity used in Box2D
        playerClimbImpulseVelocity - the climbing impulse velocity used in Box2D
        playerMaxWalkVelocity - the maximal walking velocity of the player
        playerMaxClimbVelocity - the maximal climbing velocity of the player
        currentlyEquippedWeapon - the index of the currently equipped weapon in the weapon list of the player
        playerWeaponList - the equipped weapons of the player
